    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "when you say critics argue it \"can\" strain resources, is that actually backed by data or is it more of a theoretical concern? i feel like i hear a lot about the growth benefits being a fact whereas the downsides are always presented as just \"concerns.\"",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
